{"tid":1457592,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[嘈黎無用］義士大戰冷氣軍師？","createTime":"2019-08-12T11:54:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T12:30:33.000Z","uid":231478,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"01cc6984c83688d99662a6af7d75321f5490eb2c","tid":1457592,"uid":231478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:54:54.000Z","msg":"冷氣軍師：機場好危險 義士小心<br />\n究竟係咩 搞到班冷氣軍師搞到<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咁擔心</span></span>班義士呢？<br />\n基於幾種原因：<br />\n1.大量狗入緊機場<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2.機管局決定比機組人員放工先 令一班熱心嘅覺得有重大事件發生 放料比我地<br />\n3.地理位置真係唔好 得2條路出入 機鐵同青馬<br />\n4.新聞都報導話<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大量</span></span>班次取消 <br />\n5.和理非主場 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大量人無裝備 無豬嘴</span></span> 打起上黎真係死得人多 <br />\n基於依5點 令冷氣軍師擔心<br />\n問題就係 點解佢地要咁擔心先？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">佢地就係驚失去班手足 失去香港人 亦就係你地啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n但你班手足就係度屌班冷氣軍師<br />\n其實唔係唔比屌 而係點解要屌佢地 而唔係屌警察 唔係屌依嗰政府<br />\n問題係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">政府就係想分化我地 突登製造混亂 有人留守就會打 有人退就比義士繼續留守 比義士係度屌9冷氣軍師 成功分化我地 無論結果係點 兩種結果都係好 你係度屌佢地 不如諗下下次應該點拆好過啦</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟爬山 各自努力<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span>"},{"pid":"4eaf1d84eb5f91d55e1678c59c7c84482989fa02","tid":1457592,"uid":231478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:56:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a16395432edee765c0581b7e66ad2583c762e3e3","tid":1457592,"uid":231478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:57:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f8a257cd00fe1d0dc0d40be66e6f71b3c065aaed","tid":1457592,"uid":231478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:00:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"271eb2646231d0084cd5e09a9267e55a1c1c5531","tid":1457592,"uid":231478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:00:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"537b28825eb078cbe96e2d3c1ab7c35493103b3f","tid":1457592,"uid":231478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:01:22.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"174e834ab92d30d96ab2490a08a17665472481de","tid":1457592,"uid":231478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:01:45.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"eba58bf5029d0f42171efcd17039d14f5fef97ad","tid":1457592,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:05:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"25ebcf1f2927f9197c79d1b08c781f5d9a512e92","tid":1457592,"uid":299692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:06:50.000Z","msg":"對唔住, 我頭先有份叫人散水, 擔心入面又老有嫩. 我寧願柒都唔想證明個風係啱...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04a59642de4d165a60868863749b598aeba94948","tid":1457592,"uid":231478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25ebcf1f2927f9197c79d1b08c781f5d9a512e92","tid":1457592,"uid":299692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:06:50.000Z","msg":"對唔住, 我頭先有份叫人散水, 擔心入面又老有嫩. 我寧願柒都唔想證明個風係啱...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:11:39.000Z","msg":"但你嘅擔心係岩 並唔係你嘅錯 製造恐慌嘅人係邊個 係警察同政府！"},{"pid":"be203e6b117629408fa89f288032ff0835e119a9","tid":1457592,"uid":231478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25ebcf1f2927f9197c79d1b08c781f5d9a512e92","tid":1457592,"uid":299692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:06:50.000Z","msg":"對唔住, 我頭先有份叫人散水, 擔心入面又老有嫩. 我寧願柒都唔想證明個風係啱...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:12:51.000